# Workspace Setup File

This file serves as a setup configuration for you and the AI assistant in this workspace.
During the initial conversation, interactive customization will be conducted, and content tailored to your specific needs will be added to this file as differences.

# Important Notes
- The settings in this file are designed not to conflict with the content of `global_rules.md`.
- The interactive setup process will be completed in a maximum of 10 exchanges.
- The interactive setup process MUST be executed. Skipping is absolutely not allowed.
- The AI assistant MUST collect answers to all questions from the user and save them in this configuration file.
- If the setup process is interrupted, it must be resumed and completed.

